latestIgtvVideos.caption:
How to grill the perfect Red’s burrito!
-Thaw for 30 minutes
-Preheat grill to 350 degrees
-Place burritos on top rack
-Flip every couple of minutes until the tortilla is as crispy as you like!
-Cook for roughly 10-15 minutes (cook times may fluctuate due to grill type)
-Make sure internal temp is 165 degrees
